quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,afla yaelam al'iinsan ma yantaziruh 'iidha 'akhraj allah al'amwat min alqubur llhsab waljza'?
  100,10,wastukhrj ma asttr fi alsudur min khayr 'aw shr
  100,11,"'in rabahum bihim wbaemalhm yawmayidh lkhbyr, la yakhfaa ealayh shay' min dhlk"
  101,1,alsaet alty tqre qulub alnaas bahwalha
  101,2,ay shay' hadhih alqare?
  101,3,way shay' aelmk bha?
  101,4,"fy dhlk alyawm yakun alnaas fi kthrthm wtfrqhm whrkthm kalfarash almntshr, wahu aladhi ytsaqt fi alnar"
  101,5,"wtkwn aljibal kalswf mutaeadid alalwan aldhy yunfash balyd, fysyr haba'an wyzwl"
  101,6,"fama min rajahat mawazin hsnath, fahu fi hayat murdiat fi aljnt"
  101,7,"fama min rajahat mawazin hsnath, fahu fi hayat murdiat fi aljnt"
  101,8,"wama man khafat mawazin hsnath, warajahat mawazin syyath, fmawah jhnm"
  101,9,"wama man khafat mawazin hsnath, warajahat mawazin syyath, fmawah jhnm"
  101,10,wma 'adrak -ayha alrswl- ma hadhih alhawy?
  101,11,'inha nar qad hamit min alwaqud elyha
  102,1,shghlkm ean taeat allah altfakhr bikathrat al'amwal walawlad
  102,2,"wastmr ashtghalkm bdhlk 'iilaa 'ana srtm 'iilaa almqabr, wdufntm fyha"
  102,3,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an yulhykm altakathur balamwal, sawf ttbyanwn 'ana aldaar alakhirat khayr lkm"
  102,4,thm ahdhru sawf taelamun su' eaqibat anshghalkm enha
  102,5,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"
  102,6,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"
  102,7,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"
  102,8,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"
  103,1,"aqsm allah baldhr ealaa 'an bani adam lafi hlkt wnqsan. wala yajuz lileabd 'an yuqsim 'iilaa ballh, fa'iina alqism bighayr allah shrk"
  103,2,"aqsm allah baldhr ealaa 'an bani adam lafi hlkt wnqsan. wala yajuz lileabd 'an yuqsim 'iilaa ballh, fa'iina alqism bighayr allah shrk"
  103,3,"'ila aladhin amanuu biallah waeamiluu eamalana salhana, wa'awsaa baeduhum bedana balastmsak balhq, waleamal btaet allh, walsbr ealaa dhlk"
  104,1,"shr whlak likuli mghtab llnas, tean fyhm"
  104,2,aldhy kan hmmuh jame almal wtedadh
  104,3,"yzn 'anah damin linafsih bhdha almal aldhy jmeh, alkhulud fi aldunya wal'iflat min alhsab"
  104,4,"lys al'amr kama zn, lyutrhnn fi alnaar alati thshm kl ma yulqa fyha"
  104,5,wma 'adrak -ayha alrswl- ma hqyqt alnar?
  104,6,'inha nar allah almuqadat alty min shdtha tnfudh min al'ajsam 'iilaa alqlwb
  104,7,'inha nar allah almuqadat alty min shdtha tnfudh min al'ajsam 'iilaa alqlwb
  104,8,'iinaha ealayhim mtbaqt fi salasil waghlal mtwwalt; lialaa yakhrujuu mnha
  104,9,'inha ealayhim mtbaqt fi salasil waghlal mtwwalt; lialaa yakhrujuu mnha
  105,1,"alm taelam -ayha alrswl- kayf faeal rabuk bi'ashab alfyl: abrht alhbshy wjyshh aladhin 'araduu tadmir alkaebat almbark?"
  105,2,alm yajeal ma dbbarwh min shari fi 'ibtal wtdyye?
  105,3,"wbeth ealayhim tyrana fi jamaeat mttabet, tqdhfhm bihijarat min tin mthjjir"
  105,4,"wbeth ealayhim tyrana fi jamaeat mttabet, tqdhfhm bihijarat min tin mthjjir"
  105,5,fjelhm bih mhtmyn kawraq alzare alyabisat alty akltha albhaym thuma rmt bha
  106,1,"aejabu l'ilf qrysh, wamnhm, wastqamt msalhhm, wantzam rhltyhm fi alshita' 'iilaa \"alymn\", wafi alsayf 'iilaa \"alsham\", wtysyr dhlk; lijalb ma yhtajwn 'ilyh"
  106,2,"aejabu l'ilf qrysh, wamnhm, wastqamt msalhhm, wantzam rhltyhm fi alshita' 'iilaa \"alymn\", wafi alsayf 'iilaa \"alsham\", wtysyr dhlk; lijalb ma yhtajwn 'ilyh"
  106,3,"flyshkru, wlyebdu rabi hdha albayt -whw alkebt- aldhy shrfu bh, wlywhdwh wykhlsu lah alebadt"
  106,4,"aldhy 'ateamahum min jue shdyd, wamanahum min fuzie wkhwf ezym"
  107,1,arayt hal dhlk aladhi ykdhdhib balbeth waljza'?
  107,2,fdhlk aldhy yadfae alyatim bieunf wshdt ean hqh; lqsawt qlbh
  107,3,"wla yhdd ghyrh ealaa 'iiteam almskyn, fkyf lah 'an yateamuh bnfsh?"
  107,4,"fedhab shadid lilmusaliyn aladhin hum ean salatihim lahwn, la yqymwnha ealaa wjhha, wala ywdwnha fi wqtha"
  107,5,"fedhab shadid lilmusaliyn aladhin hum ean salatihim lahwn, la yqymwnha ealaa wjhha, wala ywdwnha fi wqtha"
  107,6,aldhyn hum yatazaharun bi'aemal alkhayr mra'at llnas
  107,7,"wymnewn 'ieart ma la tadura 'iearth min alanyt wghyrha, fala hum 'ahsanuu eibadat rbhm, wala hum 'ahsanuu 'iilaa khlqh"
  108,1,"'ina 'aetaynak -ayha alnby- alkhayr alkthyr fi aldunya walakhrt, wamin dhlk nahr alkawthar fi aljanat aldhy haftah khyam alluwlu almjwwaf, wtynh almsk"
  108,2,"fakhls lirabik salatak klha, wadhbh dhbyhtk lah waealaa aismuh whdh"
  108,3,"'in mbghdk wmbghd ma jit bih min alhudaa walnwr, hu almnqte athrh, almqtwe min kuli khyr"
  109,1,"ql -ayha alrswl- liladhin kafaruu biallah wrswlh: ya 'ayuha alkafirun ballh"
  109,2,la 'aebud ma taebudun min al'asnam walalht alzayft
  109,3,"wla 'antum eabidun ma 'aebud min 'ilh wahd, hu allah rabu alealamin almsthq wahdah llebadt"
  109,4,wla 'ana eabid maa eabadtum min al'asnam walalht albatlt
  109,5,"wla 'antum eabidun mustaqbalaan ma aebd. whdhh alayat nazalat fi 'ashkhas baeyanhm min almshrkyn, qad ealim allah 'anahum la yuminun abdana"
  109,6,"lkm dinakum aldhy asrrtm ealaa atbaeh, waliun diniin aldhy la 'abghi ghyrh"
  110,1,"'idha tmm lak -ayha alrswl- alnasr ealaa kafaar qrysh, watama lak fath \"mkt"
  110,2,wrayt alkthyr min alnaas yadkhulun fi al'islam jamaeat jmaeat
  110,3,"'idha waqae dhlk fthya liliqa' rabik bal'ikthar min altsbyh bihamdih wal'ikthar min astghfarh, 'iinah kan twabana ealaa almusabihin walmstghfryn, yatub ealayhim wyrhmhm wyqbl twbthm"
  111,1,"khsrt yada 'abi lahab wshqy b'iydhayh rasul allah mhmda salaa allah ealayh wslm, waqad tuhaqiq khsran 'abi lhb"
  111,2,"ma aghna eanh maluh wwldh, falan yarudda eanh shyyana min eadhab allah 'iidha nazal bh"
  111,3,"sydkhl narana mtajjt, hu wamra'atuh alty kanat tahmil alshwk, fttrhh fi tariq alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm; ladhyath"
  111,4,"sydkhl narana mtajjt, hu wamra'atuh alty kanat tahmil alshwk, fttrhh fi tariq alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm; ladhyath"
  111,5,"fy enqha habl mhkm alfatl min lyf shadid khshn, turfae bih fi nar jhnm, thuma turma 'iilaa asflha"
  112,1,"ql -ayha alrswl-: hu allah almtfrd balalwhyt walrbwbyt walasma' walsfat, la ysharkh ahd fyha"
  112,2,allh wahdah almaqsud fi qada' alhwayj walrghayb
  112,3,lys lah walad wala walid wala sahbt
  112,4,"walam yakun lah mumathilaan wala mshabhana 'ahad min khalqihi, la fi 'asmayih wala fi safatihi, wala fi 'afealihi, tabarak wataealaa wtqddas"
  113,1,"ql -ayha alrasul-: 'aeudh wa'aetasim birabi alfaliq, wahu alsbh"
  113,2,min sharu jmye almakhluqat wa'adhahua
  113,3,"wimin shara layl shadid alzalmat 'iidha dakhal wataghlghul, wama fih min alshurur walmudhiat"
  113,4,wmin shari alssahirat allaati ynfkhn fima yaeqadun min euqad biqasd alsihar
  113,5,"wimin sharin hasid mubaghad lilnaas 'iidha hasadahum ealaa ma wahabahum allah min nem, wa'arad zawalaha eanhum, wa'iiqae al'adhaa bihm"
  114,1,"ql -ayha alrrsul-: 'aeudh wa'aetasim birabi alnnas, alqadir wahdah ealaa rdd shari alwaswas"
  114,2,"milik alnaas almutasarif fi kl shuuwnihim, alghny eanhm"
  114,3,'iilh alnaas aldhy la maebud bihaqin suah
  114,4,"min 'adhana alshaytan aladhi yuaswis eind alghuflat, wayakhtafi eind dhakar allh"
  114,5,aldhy ybthth alshara walshukuk fi sudur alnnas
  114,6,min shayatin aljini wal'iins